# Group Categories
Categories can be accessed here, and admins can update / add new ones. 
Categories can have sub-categories, they can be accessed via `categories` on a category object. There is currently only 2 levels of categories allowed. 
`parent` is either null or the category that the current category is a sub-category of.


## Categories Collection [/categories?include=includes&limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `categories`,`parent` or `all`

