## Category [/categories/id?include=includes]
Get a single Category object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Category to perform action with. Has example value.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `categories`, `parent`, or `all`

### Retrieve a Category [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

